36648>>>>>>>    Function StringToTime DateTime dtTime String sTimeString Returns DateTime
36650>>>>>>>        String sHours sMinutes sSeconds
36650>>>>>>>        
36650>>>>>>>        //  Extract parts
36650>>>>>>>        Move (Mid(sTimeString, 2, 1)) to sHours
36651>>>>>>>        Move (Mid(sTimeString, 2, 4)) to sMinutes
36652>>>>>>>        Move (Mid(sTimeString, 2, 7)) to sSeconds
36653>>>>>>>        
36653>>>>>>>        //  Set to DateTime
36653>>>>>>>        Move (DateSetHour(dtTime, (Integer(sHours)))) to dtTime
36654>>>>>>>        Move (DateSetMinute(dtTime, (Integer(sMinutes)))) to dtTime
36655>>>>>>>        Move (DateSetSecond(dtTime, (Integer(sSeconds)))) to dtTime
36656>>>>>>>        
36656>>>>>>>        Function_Return dtTime
36657>>>>>>>    End_Function
